OL,3,CRacing great Jim Clark's famous Golden
OL,4,CHelmet trophy goes on display in Duns
OL,6,FA fabled trophy given to a Scottish
OL,7,Fracing legend has gone on display in
OL,8,FDuns.
OL,10,FJim Clark received the Golden Helmet
OL,11,Fin 1965, after he won both the Formula
OL,12,FOne World Championship and the
OL,13,FIndianapolis 500 - a feat that has not
OL,14,Fbeen repeated since.
OL,16,FBorn in Fife, Clark's family Edington
OL,17,FMains Farm near Duns in 1942. The town
OL,18,Fis home to the Jim Clark Motorsport
OL,19,FMuseum, where the helmet will be on
OL,20,Fdisplay for the next three years.
