OL,4,CHelmet trophy goes on display in Duns
OL,6,FAssistant Curator Andrew Tulloch said:
OL,7,F"It's almost legendary. It's never
OL,8,Fbeen displayed before and if I hadn't
OL,9,Fseen it in books, I'd never really
OL,10,Fbelieve it existed.
OL,12,F"Over the years, myself and my team
OL,13,Fhave been asked, do you have this
OL,14,Fhelmet? and we can now say that we do.
