OL,3,CRacing great Jim Clark's famous Golden
OL,4,CHelmet trophy goes on display in Duns
OL,6,F"We've had to go to quite a lot of
OL,7,Flengths and planning to get the right
OL,8,Fkind of display case to display it in
OL,9,Fthe right manner. It's quite stunning
OL,10,Fwhen you look at it close. The
OL,11,Fphotographs in books don't do it
OL,12,Fjustice.
OL,14,F"There's not another trophy like it in
OL,15,Fthe world."
OL,17,FThe one-of-a-kind helmet was a gift
OL,18,Ffrom Esso, who were the fuel sponsor
OL,19,Fof the Lotus racing team which Clark
OL,20,Fdrove for between 1960 and 1968.
