OL,6,FIt includes a map of the world on its
OL,7,Fcrown, laden with precious stones
OL,8,Fhighlighting the places where Jim
OL,9,FClark won a Grand Prix during the 1965
OL,10,Fseason. A special blue sapphire marks
OL,11,Fhis home nation of Scotland.
